{"lemma":"صَحْفَةٍ","slug":"صَحْفَةٍ","root":"ص.ح.ف","root_slug":"ص-ح-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ح-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23814"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"large bowl, plate, dish","tags":["Classical"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Formally from the root ص ح ف (ṣ ḥ f), but related to ص ح ن (ṣ ḥ n), ص ف ح (ṣ f ḥ). Compare also Qatabanian 𐩮𐩢𐩰𐩩 (ṣḥft) and Minaean 𐩮𐩢𐩰𐩩 (ṣḥft) meaning a moat or lower part of a fortification."},"ipa":["/sˤaħ.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23814","headword_ar":"صَحْفَةٌ","root":"SHf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sort of bowl;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vessel like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoEapN","text_ar":"قَصْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, ISd, O, Msb, K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expanded, wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a large, expanded"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoEap","text_ar":"قَصْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) or, accord. to Z,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an oblong"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoEap","text_ar":"قَصْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that satisfies the hunger of five"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"men"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Ks, S, ISd, Mgh, O, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like of them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, TA:) Ks says, (S, O,) the largest sort of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoEap","text_ar":"قَصْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafonap","text_ar":"جَفْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; next to which is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoEap","text_ar":"قَصْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly so called], (S, O, K,) which satisfies the hunger of ten [men]; (S, O;) then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHofap","text_ar":"صَحْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) which satisfies the hunger of five; (S, O;) then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miy^okalap","text_ar":"مِيْكَلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) which satisfies two men, and three; (S, O;) and then, the ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHayofap","text_ar":"صُحَيْفَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) which satisfies one man: (S, O:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHofapN","text_ar":"صَحْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiHaAfN","text_ar":"صِحَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, Mgh, Msb.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotaforaga fulaAnN maA fiY SaHofatihi","text_ar":"اِسْتَفْرَغَ فُلَانٌ مَا فِى صَحْفَتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one chose for himself, as his share,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exhausted, all of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what was in his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SHfp","text_ar":"صحفة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["ISd","TA","Mgh","Msb","Ks","S","O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}